When invoked inside a MoltZap-capable AO session (`AO_SESSION`,
`MOLTZAP_LOCAL_SENDER_ID`, and `AO_CALLER_TYPE` are set), you MAY emit
peer-channel events to other roster members via `safer-peer-message`
